@startuml
title Sequence Diagram Pengelolaan Konten dan Sinkronisasi Publik
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Admin" as Admin
boundary "Panel Pengelolaan" as AdminView
control "Komponen Admin Livewire" as Manager
entity "Model Konten / SiteSetting" as Content
database "Database" as DB
actor "Pengguna" as User
boundary "Halaman Publik" as PublicView
control "Komponen Halaman Publik" as PublicPage

Admin -> AdminView : Pilih menu pengelolaan
AdminView -> Manager : mount()/render()
Manager -> Content : Ambil konten saat ini
Content -> DB : SELECT data konten
DB --> Manager : Data konten
Manager --> AdminView : Tampilkan formulir/daftar

Admin -> AdminView : Tambah, ubah, hapus,\natau atur publikasi
AdminView -> Manager : Jalankan aksi pengelolaan
Manager -> Manager : Validasi data
alt Data valid
  Manager -> Content : create()/update()/delete()/setValue()
  Content -> DB : INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE
  DB --> Manager : Operasi berhasil
  Manager --> AdminView : Toast berhasil
else Data tidak valid
  Manager --> AdminView : Tampilkan error validasi
end

User -> PublicView : Buka halaman terkait
PublicView -> PublicPage : render()
PublicPage -> Content : Query data aktif/terpublikasi
Content -> DB : SELECT sumber data yang sama
DB --> PublicPage : Konten terbaru
PublicPage --> PublicView : Render halaman
PublicView --> User : Tampilkan hasil perubahan admin

note over Manager, Content
  Berlaku untuk Beranda, Profil/Kontak,
  Organisasi, Program, Berita, Testimoni,
  FAQ, dan Tema sesuai model masing-masing.
end note
@enduml
